gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 110, Heat 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Wizards defeated the Heat, 110-108. Kyle Kuzma led the way for the Wizards with 32 points, nine rebounds and four assists, while Tyus Jones added 12 points and 16 assists in the victory. Bam Adebayo tallied 16 points and 16 rebounds for the Heat in the losing effort. The Wizards improve to 11-53 on the season, while the Heat fall to 35-29.
